{"tid":1931550,"cid":5,"subCid":11,"title":"金融瘟疫的先兆：富豪雪糕車入大埔圍村賣雪糕","createTime":"2020-03-18T08:19:15.000Z","updateTime":"2020-03-18T09:06:45.000Z","uid":48040,"like":26,"dislike":1,"uniUserReply":15,"replies":[{"pid":"c64075a1d664aad0794139d777075939d793e0c6","tid":1931550,"uid":48040,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-03-18T08:19:15.000Z","msg":"今日睇大J最新一集，《「它」竟然直接來了我們家門前?! 這是什麽狀況?!》<br />\n<a href=\"https://www.youtube.com/watch?v=GX7husbwnjY\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=https%3A%2F%2Fwww.youtube.com%2Fwatch%3Fv%3DGX7husbwnjY&d=V4yVQ1MiaEIlcmjbsyBqF%2Bbr9%2BGymSeLOXabm6KdyvY%3D&h=48bdcb5e\" target=\"_blank\">https://www.youtube.com/watch?v=GX7husbwnjY</a><br />\n一部富豪雪糕車，居然駛入大J所住的村屋區，嚇到村民紛紛走出來，以為自己有幻覺。<br />\n但原來係真的！而且司機話自己上禮拜已經入過一次，今次係第二次了。<br />\n<img src=\"https://na.cx/i/fNr7R8U.png\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fna.cx%2Fi%2FfNr7R8U.png&h=e7b96dab&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n<br />\n證明：<br />\n尖沙嘴、中環、沙田等旺區已經完全冇遊人，<br />\n只好入住宅區去賣雪糕（仲要係村屋）。<br />\n<br />\n天降異象，危機必生。<br />\n道指熔斷，雪糕車入圍村！"},{"pid":"203f184b68459d8231b3d255bef37d28e9f8888e","tid":1931550,"uid":54125,"like":0,"dislike":1,"score":-1,"citedBy":2,"replyTime":"2020-03-18T08:20:41.000Z","msg":"關叉事<br />\n個個驚瘟疫去行山/唔出街，村仲多人過旺角<br />\n邊度多人咪去邊囉"},{"pid":"e434a20b7178248150daa3a5b278866c143f72f6","tid":1931550,"uid":68689,"like":6,"dislike":0,"score":6,"quote":{"pid":"203f184b68459d8231b3d255bef37d28e9f8888e","tid":1931550,"uid":54125,"like":0,"dislike":1,"score":-1,"citedBy":2,"replyTime":"2020-03-18T08:20:41.000Z","msg":"關叉事<br />\n個個驚瘟疫去行山/唔出街，村仲多人過旺角<br />\n邊度多人咪去邊囉"},"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-03-18T08:23:22.000Z","msg":"咪係 你試下係山上面開7仔 OK<br />\n一日生意額仲多過LKF呀"},{"pid":"4beb62ee2da04edfe9b0c838928a91c59d0d6170","tid":1931550,"uid":67332,"like":2,"dislike":0,"score":2,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2020-03-18T08:25:25.000Z","msg":"試下去獅子山郊野公園/畢架山條車路上"},{"pid":"3f0b6c26e51cc535835977531c4d1398112874e6","tid":1931550,"uid":67332,"like":0,"dislike":0